* ================================================================
* SWITCH SPICE MODELS
* Voltage-Controlled Switch (VCS) and Current-Controlled Switch (CCS)
* ================================================================
* File: switches.lib
* Description: Library for voltage and current controlled switches
* ================================================================

* ================================================================
* 1. VOLTAGE-CONTROLLED SWITCH (VCS)
* ================================================================
* SPICE Element: S
* Syntax: S<name> NP NM CP CM <model_name>
*   NP, NM     : Switch terminals (output)
*   CP, CM   : Control voltage terminals
*   model_name : Switch model name
*
* Model Syntax: .MODEL <model_name> SW(Ron=<val> Roff=<val> Vt=<val> Vh=<val>)
*   Ron   : ON resistance (default: 1 Ohm)
*   Roff  : OFF resistance (default: 1/Gmin, typically 1e12 Ohms)
*   Vt    : Threshold voltage (default: 0V)
*   Vh    : Hysteresis voltage (default: 0V)
*
* Operation:
*   - If V(CP, CM) > Vt + Vh : Switch is ON (resistance = Ron)
*   - If V(CP, CM) < Vt - Vh : Switch is OFF (resistance = Roff)
*   - Between : Linear transition
* ================================================================

* --- Voltage-Controlled Switch Model Definitions ---
.MODEL SW_VCS_0V SW(Ron=0.001 Roff=1e9 Vt=0 Vh=0)
.MODEL SW_VCS_5V SW(Ron=0.001 Roff=1e9 Vt=5 Vh=0.5)
.MODEL SW_VCS_2.5V SW(Ron=0.01 Roff=1e6 Vt=2.5 Vh=0.1)

* --- Voltage-Controlled Switch Subcircuit ---
.SUBCKT VCS NP NM CP CM PARAMS: RON=0.001 ROFF=1E9 VT=0 VH=0
* NP, NM : Switch terminals
* CP, CM : Control voltage terminals
S_VCS  NP NM  CP CM  SW_VCS
.MODEL SW_VCS SW(Ron={RON} Roff={ROFF} Vt={VT} Vh={VH})
.ENDS VCS




* ================================================================
* 2. CURRENT-CONTROLLED SWITCH (CCS)
* ================================================================
* SPICE Element: W
* Syntax: W<name> N1 N2 V<name> <model_name>
*   N1, N2     : Switch terminals (output)
*   V<name>    : Name of voltage source for current sensing
*   model_name : Switch model name
*
* Model Syntax: .MODEL <model_name> ISWITCH(Ron=<val> Roff=<val> It=<val> Ih=<val>)
*   Ron   : ON resistance (default: 1 Ohm)
*   Roff  : OFF resistance (default: 1/Gmin, typically 1e12 Ohms)
*   It    : Threshold current (default: 0A)
*   Ih    : Hysteresis current (default: 0A)
*
* Operation:
*   - If I(V<name>) > It + Ih : Switch is ON (resistance = Ron)
*   - If I(V<name>) < It - Ih : Switch is OFF (resistance = Roff)
*   - Between : Linear transition
*
* IMPORTANT: Current must be measured through a voltage source!
* ================================================================

* --- Current-Controlled Switch Model Definitions ---
.MODEL SW_CCS_ON ISWITCH(Ron=0.001 Roff=1e9 It=0 Ih=0)
.MODEL SW_CCS_10MA ISWITCH(Ron=0.01 Roff=1e6 It=10M Ih=1M)
.MODEL SW_CCS_100MA ISWITCH(Ron=0.001 Roff=1e9 It=100M Ih=5M)

* --- Current-Controlled Switch Subcircuit ---
.SUBCKT CCS NP NM SP SM PARAMS: RON=0.001 ROFF=1E9 IT=0 IH=0
* NP, NM : Switch terminals
* SP, SM : Current sensing terminals (must have voltage source)
V_SENSE  SP SI  DC 0
W_CCS    NP NM  V_SENSE  SW_CCS
.MODEL SW_CCS ISWITCH(Ron={RON} Roff={ROFF} It={IT} Ih={IH})
.ENDS CCS


* ================================================================
* 3. VOLTAGE-CONTROLLED SWITCH ONE TERMINals (VCSwitch)
* ================================================================
* SPICE Element: S
* Syntax: S<name> NP NM CP <model_name>
*   NP, NM     : Switch terminals (output)
*   CP  : Control voltage terminal
*   model_name : Switch model name
*
* Model Syntax: .MODEL <model_name> SW(Ron=<val> Roff=<val> Vt=<val> Vh=<val>)
*   Ron   : ON resistance (default: 1 Ohm)
*   Roff  : OFF resistance (default: 1/Gmin, typically 1e12 Ohms)
*   Vt    : Threshold voltage (default: 0V)
*   Vh    : Hysteresis voltage (default: 0V)
*
* Operation:
*   - If V(CP) > Vt + Vh : Switch is ON (resistance = Ron)
*   - If V(CP) < Vt - Vh : Switch is OFF (resistance = Roff)
*   - Between : Linear transition
* ================================================================


* --- Voltage-Controlled Switch Subcircuit ---
.SUBCKT VCSwitch NP NM CP  PARAMS: RON=0.001 ROFF=1E9 VT=0 VH=0
* NP, NM : Switch terminals
* CP     : Control voltage terminals
S_VCS  NP NM  CP   SW_VCS
.MODEL SW_VCS SW(Ron={RON} Roff={ROFF} Vt={VT} Vh={VH})
.ENDS VCSwitch



